{
  "stem": "7094.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there was an orphan who had to get married, and she didn't hesitate to say, I don't need the coat.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She needs it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was something that it was natural, you know, it was part of a way of life.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One didn't have praises for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was an accepted form--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met, in Israel, somebody who told me the story about my family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I find it very remarkable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When my mother was born, there was another child born at that place, whose mother was very ill, and we couldn't find feeding, you know, milk, what is it called, the nurse who feeds the babies?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Midwife?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Midwife, something, who would do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my grandmother would not tell anybody in the family, and go and feed this child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the standard of hygiene was very primitive at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a very infectious disease, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she would do this, before feeding her own child, go to feed this child.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This child lives.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Israel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "High standard to follow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, because education for women was neglected, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The boys used to go to Cheder, but education for girls was very limited.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is why my father realized that something has to be done.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, during-- I mean, at the later stage-- I know you wanted to talk rather before the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During the war, I took the responsibility to maintain the whole family, because my father was taken away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother was a very gentle soul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She just couldn't fight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She just was not-- she-- she didn't have the spirit or the strength to-- to-- to fight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was responsible for the maintenance of the whole family at a very early age.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
